The paper discusses embedding models for knowledge base completion, which involves using machine learning techniques to add missing facts to a knowledge base. This topic is closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
